text: Phwk khea klaw wa “mha brisuththi phraxngkh than kar bangkhwr kæ phwk rea thi phwk rea ca yudthux phu khum khrxng xun«nxkcak phraxngkh tæthwa phraxngkh di thrng pra than pac cuy hı kæ phwk khea læa brrphburusʹ khxng phwk khea cnkrathang phwk khea di lum tx kar raluk læa phwk khea di pen hmu chn thi wibati”
